<MethodEndpoint

Endpoint that our client must call to get the information from Open Finance:
    
* Open Finance endpoint that will be requested: ```(GET /investments/{investmentId})```
    
* FamilyType: ```Investimentos - Tesouro Direto``` 
    
The response content provided by this endpoint uses the same entity as the provided on the [Open Banking Brazil Oficial Documentation](https://openfinancebrasil.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OF/pages/163513644/Informa+es+T+cnicas+-+DC+T+tulos+do+Tesouro+Direto+-+v1.0.1).
